('7570', '1', 'Spray grill with nonstick spray. Preparebarbecue (medium-high heat).'),
('7570', '2', 'Brush tuna steaks, zucchini, andeggplant with olive oil. sprinkle with saltand pepper. Grill vegetables until tenderand lightly charred, turning occasionally,about 12 minutes.'),
('7570', '3', 'Remove from grill andcut into bite-size chunks.'),
('7570', '4', 'Place vegetables,tomatoes, herbes de Provence, and garlicin large bowl. toss to blend. Set aside.Grill tuna steaks to desired doneness,about 4 minutes per side for medium-rare.'),
('7570', '5', 'Place tuna on plates, top with vegetables,and serve with aioli.* A dried herb mixture. sold in the spicesection of supermarkets and at specialtyfoods stores. If unavailable, a combinationof dried thyme, basil, savory, and fennel seeds can be substituted.'),
('7570', '6', 'Per serving: 335 calories, 15g fat (2g saturated), 63mg cholesterol, 69mg sodium, 15g carbohydrates, 7g fiber, 36g protein'),
