('7604', '1', 'Heat 1 tablespoon oil in a large skillet over medium heat.'),
('7604', '2', 'Add onion, and saut 5 minutes or until tender. Stir in garlic, and cook 1 minute.'),
('7604', '3', 'Add wine, artichokes, and capers. bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low, cover, and cook 5 minutes. Stir in tomatoes and 1/4 teaspoon salt. Cover and cook about 3 minutes or just until tomatoes are wilted.'),
('7604', '4', 'Remove from heat, and stir in parsley. Meanwhile, heat a large skillet over medium-high heat.'),
('7604', '5', 'Add remaining 2 teaspoons oil. Sprinkle tuna with peppercorns and remaining 1/4 teaspoon salt.'),
